This is a YAML configuration utility class.

Invoke it like this:

props = BW::YAMLConfig.new("onlydefault.yml",
                           "newuserfile.yml").props

                               OR

props = BW::YAMLConfig.new.props will use the default values local_properties.yml and
local_properties_default.yml

This can be useful for parameters specific to a rake build that you want users to be
able to change and thus not versioned